name: Relaxing Saxophone
description:
A relaxing saxophone. Made with AudaCity and Reaper. I added reverb and a bluesy sound in the background to an existing backtrack. The saxophone is composed from different samples from looperman. 
Looperman sounds 78638, 78325, 77896 and 75264. Credit to 'ferryterry'.
